CORE LIBRARY
	Since Version 2.1.

************************************************************
Third Party software included here:

  tclap/	-- a sophisticated "Command Line Argument Processor" (CLAP)
			from Michael Smoot.   Read the Overview inside
			"tclap-example.cpp" about CLAP.   To compile
			and test this example, you can just type:

			> make tclap

			(See the Makefile for more examples)

Files in this subdirectory, $(CORE_PATH)/third_party:
  README		-- this file
  Makefile		-- Various targets. e.g.,  try "make test"
  Make.Options		-- included by Makefile
  tclap-exampe.cpp	-- Illustrating use of tclap.

